<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="513" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,150,393]" pageId="14" pageNumber="513">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,330,356]" pageId="14" pageNumber="513">Remarks:</emphasis>
The larva of this species was described from Khandala (
<collectingRegion box="[952,1098,330,357]" country="India" name="Maharashtra" pageId="14" pageNumber="513">Maharashtra</collectingRegion>
), 
<collectingCountry box="[1117,1175,330,356]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="513">India</collectingCountry>
by Braasch (1981); we provide a supplementary larval description based on our material from south 
<collectingCountry box="[1015,1076,366,392]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="513">India</collectingCountry>
. Adult stages are unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
